This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection and image transformation techniques. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it involves designing adversarial attacks and improving the robustness of models. The paper also discusses the security and cryptography (cs.CR) aspect of object detection systems. Finally, it may belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with image and video processing.
